Water Can Delivery

Take an area : Combination of 3 or 4 streets. Tie up with local water vendors.
				
VAS : Scheduled delivery  & Online Payment (Bit Risk coz of failed delivery and payment gateway is not easy)

Pros : Easily reachable to bachelors dependent on water can.
		Easy UI 

Things to Do : Find an area where the bachelors/water can usage is more and start the pilot app there.

Cons : Convincing Shop keepers for this idea.
	   Handling repeated failed delivery of can.
	   A simple phone call can do then why an app : So this needs to be delivered immediately
	   
	   
